void execute(org.apache.sling.api.resource.ResourceResolver resourceResolver,

                  throws com.day.cq.workflow.WorkflowException
        Deprecated. use alternate method
        Process a payload path using using the provided Workflow Processes.
        Parameters:
        resourceResolver - the resourceResolver object that provides access to the JCR for WF ops
        payloadPath - the path to execute the workflow against
        workflowSteps - defines the list of WF Steps to process, each representing a WF Process
        autoSaveAfterEachWorkflowProcess - persist changes to JCR after each Workflow Process completes
        autoSaveAtEnd - persist changes to JCR after all Workflow Process complete
        Throws:
        com.day.cq.workflow.WorkflowException

      • execute

        @Deprecated
void execute(org.apache.sling.api.resource.ResourceResolver resourceResolver,
                         String payloadPath,
                         SyntheticWorkflowRunner.WorkflowProcessIdType workflowProcessIdType,
                         String[] workflowProcessIds,
                         Map<String,Map<String,Object>> processArgs,
                         boolean autoSaveAfterEachWorkflowProcess,
                         boolean autoSaveAtEnd)
                  throws com.day.cq.workflow.WorkflowException
        Deprecated. use alternate method
        Process a payload path using using the provided Workflow Processes. This is deprecated as it only allows a single workflow step of a particular process type to be executed.
        Parameters:
        resourceResolver - the resourceResolver object that provides access to the JCR for WF ops
        payloadPath - the path to execute the workflow against
        workflowProcessIdType - defines is the WF ProcessIds are process.labels or process class names
        workflowProcessIds - the process.labels or process names of the WF to execute in order against the payloadPath resource
        processArgs - the WF args metadata maps; each workflowProcessLabel can have one map
        autoSaveAfterEachWorkflowProcess - persist changes to JCR after each Workflow Process completes
        autoSaveAtEnd - persist changes to JCR after all Workflow Process complete
        Throws:
        com.day.cq.workflow.WorkflowException
